    <div id="modalExamReminder" class="fixed inset-0 bg-black/80 z-[800] hidden items-center justify-center p-4 backdrop-blur-sm">
        <div class="bg-white w-full max-w-sm rounded-[2rem] p-8 shadow-2xl text-center border-4 border-indigo-400 transform scale-100 animate-bounce-short">
            <div class="w-24 h-24 bg-indigo-50 text-indigo-500 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-5xl mx-auto mb-6 border border-indigo-100 shadow-inner">🎓</div>
            <h3 class="font-black text-gray-800 text-2xl mb-2">Pengumuman!</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mb-6 leading-relaxed font-medium">
                Selamat! Kamu sudah menyelesaikan 5 pertemuan berturut-turut. <br><br>
                Jangan lupa besok <b>Ujian <span id="examReminderSubject" class="uppercase text-indigo-600 font-black">Mapel</span></b>. <br>
                Pelajari lagi materi yang telah diajarkan ya!
            </p>
            <button onclick="closeExamReminder()" class="w-full py-4 bg-indigo-600 text-white font-black rounded-2xl shadow-lg shadow-indigo-600/30 active:scale-95 transition-all text-sm uppercase tracking-widest">
                Siap, Laksanakan!
            </button>
        </div>
